( ThorCNC - Inside Center Z-Probe )
( #3: Max XY, #4: Max Z, #5: Search Vel, #6: Probe Vel, #7: Z Cl, #8: Depth, #9: Auto Zero )

O<inside_center> sub
    ( 1. Initialization )
    G90 G17 G40 G21
    G92.1 ( Cancel any lingering G92 offsets )
    M50 P0 ( Disable Feed Override )

    ( 2. Simple Z-Probe at current location inside pocket )
    G91
    G38.2 Z-[#4] F#5
    G0 Z#7
    G38.2 Z-[#7 * 1.5] F#6

    G90 ( From here on Z is absolute in current WCS )

    ( 3. Capture surface and optional Auto-Zero )
    #<z_surface> = #5063
    O101 if [#9 GT 0.5]
        G10 L20 P0 Z0
        #<z_surface> = 0
    O101 endif
    #<z_clearance> = [#<z_surface> + #7]

    G0 Z#<z_clearance> ( Absolute raise to clearance )

    ( 4. Cleanup )
    M50 P1 ( Re-enable Feed Override )

O<inside_center> endsub
M2
